Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: UN vote condemns Soviets
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w177
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 27 Jan 1980
Hopes that massive UN vote against Soviet invasion could sway diplomatic solution. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less